> 2) How do I know the FH variable output to match to the tree?
> e.g. if mHc is mapped to MHp, how do i know what to match for mA?
Take a look at files created in dir data/FH_outputFiles/mhmax/

In FH outputs there is a line like
| MA0           =      60.50887900
The Finder class parses the value 60.50887900 if you make it search for 
"MA0".

